---
const before = [
  {
    title: 'Iklan jalan, CS libur',
    body: 'Budget iklan jalan 24/7, tapi tim CS cuma Senin-Jumat jam 9-5. Chat weekend numpuk, Senin pagi leads udah cold.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Gaji CS bengkak',
    body: 'Makin banyak chat = makin banyak hire CS. Gaji, training, turnover — costnya naik terus tiap kuartal.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Chat nyebar di 4 device',
    body: 'WhatsApp di HP admin, Instagram di HP marketing, Messenger di laptop boss. Tim kewalahan, pelanggan nunggu lama.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Data pelanggan hilang',
    body: 'Riwayat chat ada di HP pribadi CS. Kalau resign, data ikut hilang. Upsell & retention? Lupakan.',
  },
];

const after = [
  {
    title: 'AI balas 24/7, non-stop',
    body: 'Chatbot AI handle pertanyaan umum tengah malam, weekend, libur nasional. Tim CS tinggal fokus ke yang kompleks.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Hemat biaya CS hingga 60%',
    body: 'Satu agent handle volume chat 3x lebih banyak. Gak perlu hire baru tiap bisnis scaling.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Satu inbox, semua channel',
    body: 'WhatsApp, Instagram, Messenger dalam satu dashboard. Tim kerja dari satu tempat, respon cepat di semua channel.',
  },
  {
    title: 'CRM built-in, data aman',
    body: 'Setiap chat auto-tersimpan di CRM. Profil pelanggan lengkap, riwayat tertata, upsell jadi sistematis.',
  },
];
---

<section id="problem" class="relative py-20 md:py-32 bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-40 left-1/4 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-red-100/40 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-40 right-1/4 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-brand-200/30 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-mx">
    <div class="reveal mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center mb-14 md:mb-20">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-brand-200 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-700 mb-4">
        Problem → Solusi
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 leading-[1.15]">
        Dari chat berantakan ke <span class="text-gradient">bisnis yang tertata</span>.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-base md:text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        Tanpa sistem yang tepat, tiap weekend bisnis kamu bocor diam-diam. Begini bedanya sebelum dan sesudah pakai mengirim.id.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-5 lg:gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- BEFORE -->
      <div class="reveal relative rounded-3xl border border-red-200/70 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 shadow-card">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-red-50 text-red-600">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-red-600">Sebelum</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Tanpa mengirim.id</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-5">
          {
            before.map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 flex-none inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-50 text-red-600">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                    <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">{item.title}</div>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">{item.body}</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl bg-red-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-red-700">
          <strong>Boncor tiap bulan.</strong> Iklan ke-spent, leads ghosted, CS burnout.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- AFTER -->
      <div class="reveal relative rounded-3xl border-2 border-brand-300 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 shadow-glow">
        <div class="absolute -top-3 left-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-gradient px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white shadow-glow">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6.2 4.5 2.4 7.4-6.2-4.5-6.2 4.5 2.4-7.4L2 9.4h7.6z"/>
          </svg>
          Rekomendasi
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-gradient text-white shadow-glow">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-700">Sesudah</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Dengan mengirim.id</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-5">
          {
            after.map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 flex-none inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-gradient text-white">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">{item.title}</div>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">{item.body}</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl bg-brand-gradient px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white">
          <strong>ROI iklan balik, biaya CS turun.</strong> Tiap chat jadi peluang, bukan beban.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats band -->
    <div class="reveal mx-auto mt-14 md:mt-20 max-w-5xl grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 md:p-10 shadow-card">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gradient">3×</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-600 leading-tight">Volume chat per agent, tanpa nambah CS</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gradient">24/7</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-600 leading-tight">AI balas otomatis — weekend, tengah malam, libur</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gradient">&lt;1 mnt</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-600 leading-tight">Rata-rata first response time</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gradient">60%</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-600 leading-tight">Potensi hemat biaya operasional CS</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
